@startuml
title Component Diagram

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #f4f8ff
  BorderColor #1d70b8
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #fff4d6
  BorderColor #d48d00
}

actor "External Client" as Client

component "recommender-service\n(port 8083)" as Recommender
component "catalog-service\n(port 8081)" as Catalog
component "event-service\n(port 8082)" as Event
database "PostgreSQL\n(reco-db)" as Postgres

Client --> Recommender : REST (GET /recommendations,\nGET /reports,\nCRUD /strategies)
Client --> Catalog : REST (CRUD /items,\n/users,\n/ratings)
Client --> Event : REST (POST/GET /events,\nGET /events/stats/*)
Recommender --> Catalog : REST (GET /items,\nGET /items/search,\nGET /ratings,\n... )
Recommender --> Event : REST (GET /events,\nGET /events/stats,\n... )

Catalog --> Postgres : JDBC (catalog-db schema)
Event --> Postgres : JDBC (event-db schema)
Recommender --> Postgres : JDBC (recommender-db schema)

@enduml
